  "description": " **\u0026ldquo;There\u0026rsquo;s no petition we can sign to end poverty, or to make \u0026rsquo;no\u0026rsquo; a word with teeth. I know there\u0026rsquo;s not enough windows to break us a free, but maybe one would be just enough for some dignity.\u0026rdquo; **- Pat the Bunny, “A Glorious Shipwreck”\nThere were once three people who, through their patronage of the same salon, became friends. Two worked within the city\u0026rsquo;s university, and one lived just outside it.\n",
